These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, iris, lily
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who growspoppy##2
4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsiris is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsdahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | lily         | poppy   | iris | dahlia       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, r&b, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is between the person who's hobby is reading and the fan of hip-hop##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | d&b   | folk | r&b       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, videographer, lawyer, manager
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the lawyer is between the videographer and the person eating corn##2
3. the videographer is on the far left##1
4. the manager is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Job   | videographer | lawyer   | manager | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, orange, white, fuchsia
1. the person who likes orange is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who likes blue and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Color   | white | fuchsia | blue | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
City: hamburg, prague, new-york, liverpool
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to prague##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| City      | new-york | prague  | liverpool | hamburg    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
City: miami, london, paris, hannover
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to miami##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| City         | miami | hannover | london   | paris |

