.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cucumber, pumpkin, avocado
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person eating cucumber is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person eating kiwi is between the person driving the bus and the person eating pumpkin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | avocado   | cucumber | kiwi | pumpkin      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

