.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, bartender, teacher
1. the dancer is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the pilot is between the person who's sport is soccer and the bartender##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the dancer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Job   | bartender   | pilot     | teacher | dancer |

