.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, traveling, singing, writing
1. the librarian is between the person who's hobby is photography and the dressmaker##2
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Hobby   | photography         | writing       | traveling    | singing         |

