.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
House: art-deco, ranch-style, townhouse, cape-cod
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the ranch-style house is between the person eating garlic and the cape-cod house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| House   | cape-cod | ranch-style | townhouse | art-deco |

