.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, lime, onion
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, rat, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating onion and the person eating apple##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | cauliflower | onion   | lime        |
| Pet   | goldfish | rat   | horse | dog |

