2. the person traveling to prague is between the person watching sports movies and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| City           | edinburgh | prague | paris | hannover     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

