.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, firefighter, librarian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, cain, fonseca, bolivar
1. the entrepreneur is the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Cigar   | cain   | prince | bolivar         | fonseca |

