2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Beverage   | 7up    | hot-chocolate  | tea    | fanta       |

