.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
City: berlin, marseilles, hamburg, rome
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person traveling to rome is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to hamburg##2
5. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City   | rome   | berlin   | marseilles | hamburg |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

