.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, cauliflower, grapes, pepper
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apricot is between the owner of the cat and the person eating pepper##2
3. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | grapes    | pepper     | apricot | cauliflower |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 